                        .ui.basic.card
                            .content
                                h2  
                                    span#narrate-slide-header-types In person
                                p#narrate-3-types
                                    span “Shoulder surfing” – watching you from a nearby location as you enter in your telephone number or credit card number – or listening in on your conversation as you give your credit card number over the telephone.
                                    a(href='https://www.justice.gov/criminal/criminal-fraud/identity-theft/identity-theft-and-identity-fraud.' target='_blank')
