                                h2
                                    span#narrate-slide-header-types-2 Paperwork
                                p#narrate-2-types-2
                                    span If you receive an application for “pre-approved” credit cards in the mail, but discard them without tearing up the enclosed materials, scammers may retrieve them and try to activate the cards for their use without your knowledge.
                                    a(href='https://www.justice.gov/criminal/criminal-fraud/identity-theft/identity-theft-and-identity-fraud.' target='_blank')
                                        sup [1]
